# 🚀 1️⃣ Smart Link Rotation Engine (Very Technical)

Instead of showing same link always:

### Idea:

If a link has 3 variants, rotate them automatically.

Example:

* Variant A → shown 40%
* Variant B → shown 30%
* Variant C → shown 30%

### What you build:

* Weighted random selection logic
* Rotation tracking
* Impression counting
* Conversion tracking

### Why this is powerful:

Now your app becomes:

> A/B testing system for creators.

This is real SaaS-level logic.

