## ✅ Scaling Strategy for 10K Users (Free Edition)

| Problem            | Solution                                           |
| ------------------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| DB slow            | Add indexes + pagination                           |
| Feed slow          | Cache timelines in Redis                           |
| API slow           | Add rate limiting                                  |
| Server dying?      | Use horizontal scaling on free tier                |
| Storage limit?     | Move to Cloudflare R2 (free 10GB)                  |
| Free tier DB limit | Move DB to free PostgreSQL on Neon (up to 3M rows) |

---

